<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>绑定${data.result ? '成功' : '失败'}</title>
    <style>
      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .container {
        margin: 40px auto;
        width: 600px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 5px #888888;
        padding: 40px;
      }

      a.btn {
        height: 40px;
        margin: 8px 0 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        border: 0;
        cursor: pointer;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 3px;
        background-color: #705949;
        padding: 6px 18px;
        outline: 0;
        user-select: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <if(data.result)>
        $ {
          let username = data.user.username;
          username = username.substr(0, 2) + '**' + username.substr(-2, 2);
        }
        <h2>绑定成功</h2>
        <p>您的邮箱${data.email}已经成功绑定了账号${username}, 您可以通过该邮箱来找回您的密码</p>
      </if>
      <else>
        <h2>绑定失败</h2>
        <p>${data.errorMsg}</p>
      </else>
      <p><a class="btn" href="javascript:window.opener=null;window.open('','_self');window.close();">关闭页面</a></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
